
'''Valentine Uwamariya''' (wavutse ku ya 14 Gicurasi 1971) akora nka Minisitiri w’uburezi mu [[Rwanda]],<ref>https://www.un-ihe.org/news/alumna-dr-valentine-uwamariya-appointed-minister-education-rwanda</ref> <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/education-minister-back-parliament-over-ur-issues</ref>  yashyizweho na Perezida w’u [[Rwanda]] muri Gashyantare 2020.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/news/uwamariya-vows-tackle-challenges-education-sector</ref>  <ref name=":03">{{Cite news|title=Dr. Valentine UWAMARIYA {{!}} The Minister of Education|url=https://www.mineduc.gov.rw/about}}</ref>

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Valentine Uwamariya yavutse ku ya 14 Gicurasi 1971 mu Murenge wa Shangi [[Akarere ka Nyamasheke|mu Karere]] ka [[Akarere ka Nyamasheke|Nyamasheke]]. Yabonye impamyabumenyi y'amashuri yisumbuye muri Groupe Scolaire Sainte Famille, [[Akarere ka Nyamasheke|Nyamasheke]]. Yakomeje amashuri ye kandi abona impamyabumenyi ihanitse muri Chimie Organic yakuye muri [[kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda]]. <ref>https://thewaternetwork.com/member-8CG/valentine-uwamariya-KkbSFTAAtmX6xvYUQ2yxOw/home</ref>Mu 2005, Uwamariya yabonye impamyabumenyi ihanitse muri Electrochemistry yakuye muri kaminuza ya Witwatersrand muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]. Nyuma yaho, 2007, yabonye buruse yo kwiga Porogaramu ya PhD muri UNESCO-IHE naho muri 2013 abona impamyabumenyi y'ikirenga. <ref>https://www.researchgate.net/scientific-contributions/V-Uwamariya-2054738259</ref>  

== Umwuga ==
Uwamariya yabaye umuyobozi  wungirije ushinzwe amahugurwa, iterambere ry’ibigo n’ubushakashatsi muri Rwanda Polytechnic iherutse gushingwa mbere gato yuko aba Minisitiri w’uburezi.<ref>https://www.mineduc.gov.rw/about</ref>  

